episodes.title: Roman Kemp: Failed Batman auditions and being Bieber’s fixer.
episodes.description:
Tom Grennan hosts his own phone-in show!


Each week Tom and a celebrity guest open up the phone lines and answer some probing questions from callers.


This week Tom’s joined by radio host and TV presenter Roman Kemp.


They answer random questions from fans, Tom’s best friend and a member of Girls Aloud.  They discuss getting tattooed by Ed Sheeran, failed auditions, teen crushes, holiday disasters and weird experiences with celebrities.


To find out more about the podcast and future recordings check Tom’s socials:


https://www.instagram.com/tom.grennan/

https://www.facebook.com/TomGrennanMusic

https://www.tiktok.com/@tomgrennan?lang=en


The Tom Grennan Phone-in is a Banana Stand Ltd / Insanity Records Production.

episodes.title: JaackMaate: Filing a car with sewage, Sly Stallone’s lanyard and blanking Stella McCartney.
episodes.description:
Tom Grennan hosts his own phone-in show!


Each week Tom and a celebrity guest open up the phone lines to answer some probing questions from callers.


This week Tom’s joined by the YouTuber and podcaster JaackMaate. Jack is the host of his hugely successful ‘Happy Hour’ podcast and his YouTube channel has more than a million subscribers.


On this first episode they answer random questions from fans, Tom’s makeup artist, a former Premier League Footballer and Tom’s Dad.  They discuss eccentric family members, terrible first dates, driving disasters, embarrassing moments with celebrities, awkward podcast interviews and Jack's clash with the law.


To find out more about the podcast and future recordings check Tom’s socials:

episodes.title: The Tom Grennan Phone-in: launching 19th Jan!
episodes.description:
A brand new podcast coming 19th January.


Tom Grennan hosts his own phone-in show!


Each week Tom and his celebrity guest will answer probing questions from anyone - expect calls from fans, friends, Premier League footballers, members of Girls Aloud and Tom’s dad!


No subjects are off-limits so tune in for exclusive revelations about failed auditions, weird interactions with celebs, awkward kisses and disastrous holidays.


Joining Tom Grennan to answer your inappropriate questions will be Vicky McClure, Roman Kemp, Jaackmaate and Zara McDermott.


The Tom Grennan Phone-in is a Banana Stand Ltd / Insanity Records Production.
